title: Any alternatives to League website match history?
body: My league of legends match history has been down for a fucking week now and I'm just trying to see what I do...

replies.body: For future reference, OP.gg works as well.

I was able to look at your[ match history ](http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-history/NA1/210736869)without any issues.  If you're still having issues with this, [clearing your cache ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies)or running on incognito might help in case of a browser issue.  Hope that helps!

Wow thank you....
I'm actually kinda angry still because when I sent a ticket to Riot Support I got "we're working on it" without any ways to try and fix it thanks
